July 27, 2017 8:18 AM ET
Consumer Finance

Company Overview of Caterpillar Financial Services Corporation



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Caterpillar Financial Services Corporation, together with its subsidiaries, provides retail and wholesale financing alternatives for Caterpillar Inc.’s (Caterpillar) products to customers and dealers worldwide. Its retail financing includes financing of Caterpillar equipment, machinery, and engines. The company also provides financing for vehicles, power generation facilities, and marine vessels primarily for Caterpillar products. In addition, it offers wholesale financing to Caterpillar dealers; and purchases short-term receivables from Caterpillar. The company was founded in 1981 and is headquartered in Nashville, Tennessee. Caterpillar Financial Services Corporation is a subsidiary of Cat...
Caterpillar Financial Services Corporation, together with its subsidiaries, provides retail and wholesale financing alternatives for Caterpillar Inc.’s (Caterpillar) products to customers and dealers worldwide. Its retail financing includes financing of Caterpillar equipment, machinery, and engines. The company also provides financing for vehicles, power generation facilities, and marine vessels primarily for Caterpillar products. In addition, it offers wholesale financing to Caterpillar dealers; and purchases short-term receivables from Caterpillar. The company was founded in 1981 and is headquartered in Nashville, Tennessee. Caterpillar Financial Services Corporation is a subsidiary of Caterpillar Inc.
Detailed Description


2120 West End AvenueNashville, TN 37203United StatesFounded in 19811,811 Employees



